## 🔧 Manual Steps Still Required

### Step 1 — Install Mosquitto MQTT
1. Download from: https://mosquitto.org/download/ (Windows x64)
2. Run installer (installs as a Windows service automatically)
3. Copy the prepared config:
```powershell
Copy-Item C:\MyFiles\AgroMindAI\mosquitto.conf "C:\Program Files\mosquitto\mosquitto.conf" -Force
net stop mosquitto
net start mosquitto
```
4. Verify: `netstat -ano | findstr :1883` → should show a LISTENING entry

